{"tha-ap487:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap487:0.2":"Pamsukulavagga ","tha-ap487:0.3":"Candanamaliyattheraapadana ","tha-ap487:1.1":"“Panca kamagune hitva, ","tha-ap487:1.2":"piyarupe manorame; ","tha-ap487:1.3":"Asitikotiyo hitva, ","tha-ap487:1.4":"pabbajim anagariyam. ","tha-ap487:2.1":"Pabbajitvana kayena, ","tha-ap487:2.2":"papakammam vivajjayim; ","tha-ap487:2.3":"Vaciduccaritam hitva, ","tha-ap487:2.4":"nadikule vasamaham. ","tha-ap487:3.1":"Ekakam mam viharantam, ","tha-ap487:3.2":"buddhasettho upagami; ","tha-ap487:3.3":"Naham janami buddhoti, ","tha-ap487:3.4":"akasim patisantharam. ","tha-ap487:4.1":"Karitva patisantharam, ","tha-ap487:4.2":"namagottamapucchaham; ","tha-ap487:4.3":"‘Devatanusi gandhabbo, ","tha-ap487:4.4":"adu sakko purindado. ","tha-ap487:5.1":"Ko va tvam kassa va putto, ","tha-ap487:5.2":"mahabrahma idhagato; ","tha-ap487:5.3":"Virocesi disa sabba, ","tha-ap487:5.4":"udayam suriyo yatha. ","tha-ap487:6.1":"Sahassarani cakkani, ","tha-ap487:6.2":"pade dissanti marisa; ","tha-ap487:6.3":"Ko va tvam kassa va putto, ","tha-ap487:6.4":"katham janemu tam mayam; ","tha-ap487:6.5":"Namagottam pavedehi, ","tha-ap487:6.6":"samsayam apanehi me. ","tha-ap487:7.1":"Namhi devo na gandhabbo, ","tha-ap487:7.2":"namhi sakko purindado; ","tha-ap487:7.3":"Brahmabhavo ca me natthi, ","tha-ap487:7.4":"etesam uttamo aham. ","tha-ap487:8.1":"Atito visayam tesam, ","tha-ap487:8.2":"dalayim kamabandhanam; ","tha-ap487:8.3":"Sabbe kilese jhapetva, ","tha-ap487:8.4":"patto sambodhimuttamam’. ","tha-ap487:9.1":"Tassa vacam sunitvaham, ","tha-ap487:9.2":"idam vacanamabravim; ","tha-ap487:9.3":"‘Yadi buddhoti sabbannu, ","tha-ap487:9.4":"nisida tvam mahamune. ","tha-ap487:10.1":"Tamaham pujayissami, ","tha-ap487:10.2":"dukkhassantakaro tuvam’; ","tha-ap487:10.3":"Pattharitva jinacammam, ","tha-ap487:10.4":"adasi satthuno aham. ","tha-ap487:11.1":"Nisidi tattha bhagava, ","tha-ap487:11.2":"sihova girigabbhare; ","tha-ap487:11.3":"Khippam pabbatamaruyha, ","tha-ap487:11.4":"ambassa phalamaggahim. ","tha-ap487:12.1":"Salakalyanikam puppham, ","tha-ap487:12.2":"Candananca maharaham; ","tha-ap487:12.3":"Khippam paggayha tam sabbam, ","tha-ap487:12.4":"Upetva lokanayakam. ","tha-ap487:13.1":"Phalam buddhassa datvana, ","tha-ap487:13.2":"salapupphamapujayim; ","tha-ap487:13.3":"Candanam anulimpitva, ","tha-ap487:13.4":"avandim satthuno aham. ","tha-ap487:14.1":"Pasannacitto sumano, ","tha-ap487:14.2":"vipulaya ca pitiya; ","tha-ap487:14.3":"Ajinamhi nisiditva, ","tha-ap487:14.4":"sumedho lokanayako. ","tha-ap487:15.1":"Mama kammam pakittesi, ","tha-ap487:15.2":"hasayanto mamam tada; ","tha-ap487:15.3":"‘Imina phaladanena, ","tha-ap487:15.4":"gandhamalehi cubhayam. ","tha-ap487:16.1":"Pancavise kappasate, ","tha-ap487:16.2":"devaloke ramissati; ","tha-ap487:16.3":"Anunamanasankappo, ","tha-ap487:16.4":"vasavatti bhavissati. ","tha-ap487:17.1":"Chabbisatikappasate, ","tha-ap487:17.2":"manussattam gamissati; ","tha-ap487:17.3":"Bhavissati cakkavatti, ","tha-ap487:17.4":"caturanto mahiddhiko. ","tha-ap487:18.1":"Vebharam nama nagaram, ","tha-ap487:18.2":"vissakammena mapitam; ","tha-ap487:18.3":"Hessati sabbasovannam, ","tha-ap487:18.4":"nanaratanabhusitam. ","tha-ap487:19.1":"Eteneva upayena, ","tha-ap487:19.2":"samsarissati so bhave; ","tha-ap487:19.3":"Sabbattha pujito hutva, ","tha-ap487:19.4":"devatte atha manuse. ","tha-ap487:20.1":"Pacchime bhave sampatte, ","tha-ap487:20.2":"brahmabandhu bhavissati; ","tha-ap487:20.3":"Agara abhinikkhamma, ","tha-ap487:20.4":"anagari bhavissati; ","tha-ap487:20.5":"Abhinnaparagu hutva, ","tha-ap487:20.6":"nibbayissatinasavo’. ","tha-ap487:21.1":"Idam vatvana sambuddho, ","tha-ap487:21.2":"sumedho lokanayako; ","tha-ap487:21.3":"Mama nijjhayamanassa, ","tha-ap487:21.4":"pakkami anilanjase. ","tha-ap487:22.1":"Tena kammena sukatena, ","tha-ap487:22.2":"cetanapanidhihi ca; ","tha-ap487:22.3":"Jahitva manusam deham, ","tha-ap487:22.4":"tavatimsamagacchaham. ","tha-ap487:23.1":"Tusitato cavitvana, ","tha-ap487:23.2":"nibbattim matukucchiyam; ","tha-ap487:23.3":"Bhoge me unata natthi, ","tha-ap487:23.4":"yamhi gabbhe vasamaham. ","tha-ap487:24.1":"Matukucchigate mayi, ","tha-ap487:24.2":"annapananca bhojanam; ","tha-ap487:24.3":"Matuya mama chandena, ","tha-ap487:24.4":"nibbattati yadicchakam. ","tha-ap487:25.1":"Jatiya pancavassena, ","tha-ap487:25.2":"pabbajim anagariyam; ","tha-ap487:25.3":"Oropitamhi kesamhi, ","tha-ap487:25.4":"arahattamapapunim. ","tha-ap487:26.1":"Pubbakammam gavesanto, ","tha-ap487:26.2":"orena naddasam aham; ","tha-ap487:26.3":"Timsakappasahassamhi, ","tha-ap487:26.4":"mama kammamanussarim. ","tha-ap487:27.1":"Namo te purisajanna, ","tha-ap487:27.2":"namo te purisuttama; ","tha-ap487:27.3":"Tava sasanamagamma, ","tha-ap487:27.4":"pattomhi acalam padam. ","tha-ap487:28.1":"Timsakappasahassamhi, ","tha-ap487:28.2":"yam buddhamabhipujayim; ","tha-ap487:28.3":"Duggatim nabhijanami, ","tha-ap487:28.4":"buddhapujayidam phalam. ","tha-ap487:29.1":"Kilesa jhapita mayham, ","tha-ap487:29.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap487:29.3":"viharami anasavo. ","tha-ap487:30.1":"Svagatam vata me asi, ","tha-ap487:30.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap487:30.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam. ","tha-ap487:31.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap487:31.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap487:31.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap487:32.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma candanamaliyo thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap487:33.1":"Candanamaliyattherassapadanam pancamam. "}